summary: Just a preset of my current character, since she finally seem a bit more realistic.
descriptionHtml:
Just a preset of my current character, since she finally seem a bit more realistic.

Requirements:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url] (obviously)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35474/?]Ningheim race[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?]KS Hairdos - HDT Physics[/url]

Optional:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?]Freckle Mania[/url]
[url=http://www.mediafire.com/download/s3kqly25ctd63f8/The+Eyes+of+Beauty+-+The+Ningheim+compatible+version.rar]The Ningheim - TheEyesOfBeauty[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60769/?]Stoja's Warpaints
[/url]

Probably shouldn't be anything else important... for skin texture, I don't even remember which one I'm using, probably SG.
Sorry for crappy screenshot, my poor old laptop can't handle even proper shadows, let alone ENB. (if anyone likes her enough to decide to upload a picture of her with much better graphics, I'll only be happy about it)

PS: If her face looks a bit asymetrical, it's because I set it that way (although I don't know if the preset actually saves that) - her left eye is a tiny bit squinted and the 'mood' is set to slightly surprised, so her face doesn't look so plastic. HOPEFULLY.
author: peregrine111
